  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>An continental buffet breakfast serves fresh fruits, pastries, cereals, teas and coffee. Half board is available for a supplement and you'll have a choice of four courses from the menu. </p>
<p><span><strong>The Main Restaurant</strong> has a spacious terrace and large windows that overlook the Gulf of Tigullio and the promontory of Santa Margherita. The chef offers a variety of menus that focus on typical Ligurian cuisine. </span></p>
<p><strong>Restaurant pied dans l’eau</strong> is right on the beach and serves an a la carte menu of dishes such as grilled seafood, fresh salad and pasta. It is open all day from around May to September, weather permitting.</p>
<p><strong>Snack Bar</strong> overlooking the bay serving drinks and light snacks.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
